languages.text: "У судьбы паршивое чувство юмора. Из всех закоулков галактики нарваться на комиссара я умудрилась в Темном городе". {n}Джай недобро хмыкает.{/n} "Слава Великому, он сейчас очень-очень занят вопросами выживания".

"Fate has a twisted sense of humour. Of all the grubby corners in the galaxy, I've somehow managed to run into a Commissar in the Dark City." {n}Jae scoffs.{/n} "Praise be to the Exalted One, He must be very, very busy right now trying to keep me alive."

languages.text: 「運命って、悪趣味なユーモアのセンス持ちだね。なんとまあ薄汚いこの銀河の端で、仄暗き都のコミッサーにばったり出くわすなんてどういうわけだい」{n}ジェイは自嘲する。{/n}「エグザルテッド・ワンを称えよ、今ごろアタシを生かしておこうと多忙を極めてるに違いないんだから」

languages.text: “命运的玩笑真是无常啊。整个银河系有这么多蝇营狗苟的角落，可我却偏偏在黑暗之城里遇到了一位政委。”{n}婕伊自嘲地笑了。{/n}“赞美至高无上的神皇，祂老人家想必正在绞尽脑汁思考，要怎么做才能保住我的小命。”
languages.original_text: "Fate has a twisted sense of humour. Of all the grubby corners in the galaxy, I've somehow managed to run into a Commissar in the Dark City." {n}Jae scoffs.{/n} "Praise be to the Exalted One, He must be very, very busy right now trying to keep me alive."

languages.text: « Le destin a un sens de l'humour bien particulier. De tous les recoins miteux de la galaxie que j'ai pu visiter, il a fallu que je tombe sur un commissaire dans la Cité Crépusculaire. {n}Jae ricane.{/n} Loué soit l'Exalté qui doit être débordé en ce moment pour tenter d'assurer ma survie. »
languages.original_text: "Fate has a twisted sense of humour. Of all the grubby corners in the galaxy, I've somehow managed to run into a Commissar in the Dark City." {n}Jae scoffs.{/n} "Praise be to the Exalted One, He must be very, very busy right now trying to keep me alive."

languages.text: «Tiene narices el sentido del humor del destino. De todos los rincones mugrientos de la galaxia, voy y me encuentro a un comisario en la Ciudad Siniestra». {n}Jae se mofa.{/n} «Alabado sea el Exaltado, porque se tiene que estar dejando la piel en mantenerme con vida».
languages.original_text: "Fate has a twisted sense of humour. Of all the grubby corners in the galaxy, I've somehow managed to run into a Commissar in the Dark City." {n}Jae scoffs.{/n} "Praise be to the Exalted One, He must be very, very busy right now trying to keep me alive."

languages.text: "Das Schicksal hat einen seltsamen Sinn für Humor. Von all den zwielichtigen Ecken der Galaxie laufe ich ausgerechnet in der Dunklen Stadt einem Kommissar über den Weg." {n}Jae schnaubt.{/n} "Der Erhabene sei gepriesen, Er muss im Moment alle Hände voll zu tun haben, um mich am Leben zu halten."
languages.original_text: "Fate has a twisted sense of humour. Of all the grubby corners in the galaxy, I've somehow managed to run into a Commissar in the Dark City." {n}Jae scoffs.{/n} "Praise be to the Exalted One, He must be very, very busy right now trying to keep me alive."

languages.text: "Kaderin cilvesine bak. Galaksideki onca iğrenç yerde bulundum, bunun üzerine gidip Kara Şehir'de bir Komiser'e denk geliyorum." {n}Jae yüzünü buruşturuyor.{/n} "Görkemli'ye şükürler olsun. Beni hayatta tutmak için ne çok çabalıyor."
languages.original_text: "Fate has a twisted sense of humour. Of all the grubby corners in the galaxy, I've somehow managed to run into a Commissar in the Dark City." {n}Jae scoffs.{/n} "Praise be to the Exalted One, He must be very, very busy right now trying to keep me alive."

traits.locale_text: "Kaderin cilvesi işte. Galaksinin tüm pis kıyı köşeleri içinden bir şekilde Kara Şehir'de bir Komiser ile karşılaşmayı başardım." {n}Jae yüzünü buruşturuyor.{/n} "Görkemli'ye şükürler olsun. Şu anda beni hayatta tutmak için çok çabalıyor olmalı."
traits.speaker: JaeCompanion
